\c 4
\s Umkhuleko wakusihlwa wokucela uncedo
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. Ngamachacho. Isihlabelelo sikaDavida
\p
\v 1 Ngiphendula ekukhaleni kwami, Nkulunkulu wokulunga kwami. Ekucindezelweni wangenzela indawo ebanzi. Woba lomusa kimi, uzwe umkhuleko wami\x + Jobe 36.16. Hlab. 66.14.\x*.
\v 2 Madodana abantu, koze kube nini \add liphendula\add* udumo lwami lube lihlazo, lithanda okuyize, lidinga amanga? \w Sela\w**\x + Hlab. 5.6.\x*.
\v 3 Kodwa yazini ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* izehlukanisele\x + Eks. 11.7.\x* owesaba uNkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 50.5.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* iyangizwa lapho ngikhala kuyo.
\v 4 Thuthumelani, lingoni\x + Efe. 4.26.\x*; khulumani\x + Hlab. 77.6.\x* lenhliziyo yenu embhedeni wenu, lithule. \w Sela\w**\x + Hlab. 149.5.\x*.
\v 5 Nikelani imihlatshelo yokulunga\x + Dute. 33.19. Hlab. 50.14. Hlab. 51.19.\x*, lithembe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Hlab. 25.2.\x*.
\v 6 Banengi abathi: Ngubani ozasitshengisa okuhle? N\nd kosi\nd*, phakamisela\x + Hlab. 31.16.\x* ukukhanya kobuso bakho phezu kwethu\x + Hlab. 80.3,7,19. 119.135. Hlab. 89.15.\x*.
\v 7 Ubeke intokozo enhliziyweni yami\x + Isa. 9.3.\x* okwedlula isikhathi lapho amabele abo lewayini labo elitsha kwandile\x + Hos. 2.8.\x*.
\v 8 Ngizacambalala\x + Jobe 17.16.\x* ngokuthula\x + Jobe 11.18,19. Hlab. 3.5.\x*, khonokho ngilale ubuthongo, ngoba wena N\nd kosi\nd* wedwa uyangihlalisa ngokulondolozeka\x + Levi 25.18,19. 26.5. Jobe 11.18. Dute. 12.10.\x*.